{
  "texts": [
    "Parameter privacyIn federated learning, protecting client-specific parameters is crucial because ensuring the privacy of these parameters also indirectly safeguards client data privacy.",
    "As a modular approach to adjusting personalized parameters, LoRA can be effectively integrated into federated learning systems to achieve parameter privacy protection.",
    "Literature [107] proposes a secure distributed language model training framework based on model slicing.",
    "They deploy LoRA in a Trusted Execution Environment (TEE) and use OTP encryption to transmit features between the GPU and TEE, protecting model parameter privacy.",
    "PrivateLoRA [108] introduces a distributed system based on LoRA."
  ]
}